# 🍽️ Restaurant Delivery Application (Java)

This project is a Java-based desktop application developed to simplify restaurant order and delivery management through an organized and user-friendly system.

## Key Features
- User registration and secure login  
- Restaurant menu management (meals and drinks)  
- Order placement and tracking  
- Payment handling (cash / card)  
- Customer and employee management  
- Delivery service based on location  

## Technologies Used
- Java Programming  
- Java Swing (GUI)  
- MySQL Database  
- JDBC Connectivity  
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)  

## Main Concepts Applied
- Graphical User Interface design  
- Database integration  
- Data validation  
- Event handling  
- Modular programming  

## Project Goal
The main goal of this project is to improve restaurant delivery services by making order processing faster, easier, and more efficient.

